1. “Teach me [topic] like I’m ambitious—not clueless. No fluff, just gold.”
→ 5 minutes = more value than most paid courses.

2. “What are 5 truths about [topic] that experts rarely share?”
→ Surface info is free. This digs deeper.

3. “Create a 14-day learning sprint to master [skill]—1 hour per day max.”
→ No rabbit holes. Just structure that sticks.

4. “Compare the top 3 frameworks for achieving [goal]—with pros, cons, and when to use each.”
→ Not just what works—what works for you.

5. “Summarize the 3 best books on [topic] into actionable takeaways.”
→ Read less. Apply more.

6. “Turn this long tutorial into a checklist I can follow—step by step.”
→ No fluff. Just flow.

7. “Quiz me on what I’ve learned—focus on my weak spots.”
→ Feedback that forges mastery.